title: Squaremouth Announces the Top Travel Insurance Providers of August, 2015
text:
Squaremouth
ST. PETERSBURG, Fla. , Sept. 4, Squaremouth , America's fastest growing travel insurance comparison site, announced its top-selling travel insurance providers of August, 2015.
Top-Selling Travel Insurance Providers for August, 2015, Ranked by Premium Sold:
1 - AXA Assistance USA - $228,655.00
2 - InsureandGo USA - $224,817.51
3 - Tin Leg - $213,835.00
4 - RoamRight - $121,006.77
5 - Travel Insured International - $85,526.00

ABOUT SQUAREMOUTH:
Squaremouth is an online company that compares travel insurance products from virtually every major travel insurance provider in the United States . Using Squaremouth's comparison engine and third party customer reviews, travelers can research and compare insurance products side-by-side. More information can be found at www.squaremouth. com .
